### Finished TaskPrologue

Monitored the experiments and took one recovery action.

`3564074_12` was idle after Ray package upload for nearly 4 hours, with only about 9 CPU-minutes and no `SynthTaskRunner` progress. I cancelled it. Its dependent retry `3564075_12` started immediately and reached `SynthTaskRunner`, so it is no longer showing the same idle pattern.

I submitted one extra dependent continuation wave for the same row:

`3564344` with `--array=12-12%1`, dependent on `3564076`.

I also updated `3561188` so full merge/eval waits on `3564344` as well. Reward-only pass@k `3564081` is progressing normally, and the main recovery wave `3563089` is still making training progress.

